{"tid":884900,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世] m$維修苦主","createTime":"2018-11-01T03:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T07:38:56.000Z","uid":34033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"35c241ab4488e1c232a2efab71f97b1207925765","tid":884900,"uid":34033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:06:46.000Z","msg":"上個月發現部SP4開始有螢幕震嘅問題<br />\n上網發現原來好多人都有同樣問題，有得免費回收，即刻打去hotline，安排換機<br />\n<br />\n但自從10月2號收左機之後，到而家都未有消息幾時收返部機<br />\n日日打去hotline問 職員只係話未有貨/未寄出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n又冇其他替代方案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個月日日要係office、圖書館借電腦做野<br />\n真係慘撚過cut有線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通真係等到部機變磚先俾返我？<br />\n<br />\n終於明白點解m$唔set up service center，如果有一定日日有大量苦主佔領<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望大家引以為鑑，唔好重蹈覆轍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 有冇人同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8170b55bb9a72d6ec97a46da91931828abcec0ed","tid":884900,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:09:23.000Z","msg":"抵死啦索狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336afe58cb82460df30b3ddc82183b01ef638488","tid":884900,"uid":34033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8170b55bb9a72d6ec97a46da91931828abcec0ed","tid":884900,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:09:23.000Z","msg":"抵死啦索狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T07:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}